lead_paragraph: David Freese of the Pirates got the first hit of the new Major League Baseball season and Toronto star Troy Tulowitzki hit the first home run.

headline.print_headline: Freese Gets 1st Hit of New MLB Season, Tulowitzki Has 1st HR
